{"tid":2377345,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「地上最強老豆」連恩尼遜宣布退休日，感嘆自己老了：「不再接演動作片⋯」","createTime":"2021-01-23T14:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T06:56:58.000Z","uid":105567,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d34f3b4d4825d50e6174d88769f91c9f25236b53","tid":2377345,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.juksy.com/archives/106352?fbclid=IwAR1fGesY0zXiRXgKy_8m8V3xDT7KvWPiymfrX7ch1XoqH3VWx9AFQe-XDOY&amp;utm_campaign=new&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=fb_juksy&amp;utm_term=80d00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F106352%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1fGesY0zXiRXgKy_8m8V3xDT7KvWPiymfrX7ch1XoqH3VWx9AFQe-XDOY%26utm_campaign%3Dnew%26utm_content%3Dlink%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfb_juksy%26utm_term%3D80d00&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=253651b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.juksy.com/archives/106352?fbclid=IwAR1fGesY0zXiRXgKy_8m8V3xDT7KvWPiymfrX7ch1XoqH3VWx9AFQe-XDOY&amp;utm_campaign=new&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=fb_juksy&amp;utm_term=80d00</a><br />\n<br />\n出生於英國北愛爾蘭男演員連恩尼遜（Liam Neeson）毫無疑問是一代好萊塢動作片巨星，不過也由於他演出的招牌電影系列《即刻救援》（Taken）總是上山下海四處大展主角威能進行「不可能的救援任務」而廣獲台灣影迷封為是地表最強老爸。不過現在正宣傳熱騰騰在台灣上映的全新動作大片《捍衛救援》（The Marksman）之時，連恩尼遜也宣布了自己要從動作片退休的時間點！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/106352/800x_100_w-6007922c5eb33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F106352%2F800x_100_w-6007922c5eb33.jpg&h=f7d8287f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《捍衛救援》由連恩尼遜飾演海軍陸戰隊退役的神射手吉姆，原本在農莊過著退休生活的他因目睹一樁慘案而決定帶著年僅 11 歲米格爾橫跨半個美國，面對窮追不捨的毒販殺手，吉姆一路上將運用自己過去在海軍陸戰隊習得的戰鬥技巧，與這群殺手展開一場生死之戰。連恩尼遜在 etonline 宣傳新片之時，就談到了自己要退休、不再主演動作片的意願：「我現在已經 68 歲半，今年就要滿 69 歲了，我手上還有幾部片要在今年完成，希望疫情不會影響到這些作品的拍攝，但隨著這些案子完成之後，我想我就不會再繼續接演下去了。」<br />\n<br />\n連恩尼遜吐露他希望在今年內完成手上所有的動作片，接下來在 2022 年開始就從一線動作片演員陣容中引退，雖然他曾說過：「我熱愛這種可以痛扁一群小子的電影」，但年紀已經即將邁入 70 歲的他也表明現在拍動作戲時常會喘到很難受。連恩尼遜這項宣傳也代表著「地表最強老爸」我們將會看一部少一部，大家可要珍惜即日起已經在全台上映的新作《捍衛救援》！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/106352/800x_100_w-6007922cedba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F106352%2F800x_100_w-6007922cedba6.jpg&h=1e69ca27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f13d0501fbabd04bdbf75e226c1824377d24d84","tid":2377345,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f0a2d01353b83f405dac2ba42a2892997eb922","tid":2377345,"uid":49853,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"完全唔似就70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1062950639819dd5a9f8facd2ca67eaa4b733b","tid":2377345,"uid":17619,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1207869079450554368/jsY4ZAUh_400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F1207869079450554368%2FjsY4ZAUh_400x400.jpg&h=b4f8e4a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e7e14188108240ebfaa33a16a9fcb04a86867a","tid":2377345,"uid":47905,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"50尾先開始狂拍動作片<br />\n不過佢拍既動作片真係套套都唔差<br />\n幾鍾意睇佢"},{"pid":"d9cad270700da63440ccc4f0d2fc604b4ffcee77","tid":2377345,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"高大型佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19a68d7102789b7dd976404d329f74f286db3f1","tid":2377345,"uid":238819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47e7e14188108240ebfaa33a16a9fcb04a86867a","tid":2377345,"uid":47905,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:17:16.000Z","m